{
  "stem": "353.4",
  "chunk_idx": 2,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "How he said you're going to be free now, and I have to run because if the Czechs would have got him, they would hang him up-- on the-- on a tree.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So, so what I want to say is, he could have-- he could have smashed the underground group what was in-- in Brinnlitz, but he didn't So and other things what I know was done is, that we, on the end of the war was very hard with food.",
      "word_count": 49
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So he used to take a truck and go on the front where a horse was killed, he picked them up and brought to the kitchen.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And he said, here's a horse-- do whatever you want, people need to eat something.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "He was unbelievable.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "The Russians, you were liberated by the Russians?",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Then came a day what he left.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He took with him five men whom he chose and they had to be sure that he would not be arrested.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And Schindler's list-- I have it here I'm going to show how this looks.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "He took the whole Schindler's list, every name with him.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "If a-- whoever would catch him, so he had show that he saved some-- some people.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So he took five or six, I don't remember, five or six people with him.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "They should to be sure that he is in good hands.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And he went to Germany, from Czechoslovakia to Germany.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And he got-- got arrested some place [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] near Switzerland.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "I don't remember the name.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "When the Russians came, first came one Russian on a horse, and he saw that it's a concentration camp.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "There was not a factory but he saw that we are in striped uniform.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The date was 5th of-- 5th-- 9th of May, 9th of May.",
      "word_count": 12
    }
  ],
